# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
#  We'll Share — Monorepo .gitignore
#  Covers: Angular Frontend + Spring Boot Backend
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Claude AI session files ───────────────────────────────
.claude/

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  BACKEND  (Spring Boot / Maven)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Maven build output — never commit compiled bytecode
ridemate-backend/target/

# ⚠️  SECRETS — application.properties has DB password,
#     JWT secret, email credentials. DO NOT commit.
ridemate-backend/src/main/resources/application.properties
ridemate-backend/src/main/resources/application-prod.properties
ridemate-backend/src/main/resources/application-dev.properties

# User uploaded files (runtime data, not source code)
ridemate-backend/uploads/

# IntelliJ IDEA project files
ridemate-backend/.idea/
ridemate-backend/*.iml
ridemate-backend/*.iws
ridemate-backend/*.ipr
ridemate-backend/.mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.jar

# Maven wrapper (optional — keep if your team uses it)
# ridemate-backend/.mvn/

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  FRONTEND  (Angular / Node)
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Dependencies — run npm install after cloning
ridemate-frontend/node_modules/

# Angular build output
ridemate-frontend/dist/
ridemate-frontend/tmp/
ridemate-frontend/out-tsc/
ridemate-frontend/bazel-out/

# Angular CLI cache
ridemate-frontend/.angular/

# Angular prod environment (has production API URL)
ridemate-frontend/src/environments/environment.prod.ts
ridemate-frontend/src/environments/environment.development.ts

# Testing & coverage
ridemate-frontend/coverage/

# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  COMMON
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Environment / secret files
.env
.env.*
*.env
*.local
secrets.properties

# IDE & Editor
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
*.sublime-workspace
.history/
.settings/
.project
.classpath

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
ehthumbs.db

# Logs
*.log
logs/
npm-debug.log
yarn-error.log

# Archives
*.zip
*.tar.gz
*.jar
!ridemate-backend/target/*.jar
